    <h1 class="fs-3x fw-bolder">Guiding Example</h1>
    <div class="row my-3 gx-10">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p class="fw-bold fs-3" style="color: #c9a700 !important;">
                Example 1: An Australian from Sydney Australia chooses to book Vietnam South tour line.
            </p>
            <p>
                The itinerary: Saigon - Mui Ne – Nha Trang – Quy Nhon – Buon Ma Thuot – Da Lat – Saigon.<br>The
                circular tour line starts from Ho Chi Minh City on very Monday and finishes at Ho Chi Minh City the
                next Tue, 1 day more than any other standard tour line.<br>Number of participants: 1<br>Length of
                the tour: 8 days (1 day more than the standard) .<br>He flies in from Sydney to Saigon 1 day before
                the tour starts.<br>He decides to arrange Pre/ Post tour hotels and transfers for himself.<br>The
                Participant is not able to find any roommate to share then he decides to book the tour on single hotel
                room. <br>How and when to join in with the tour group: He needs to arrange transport from his
                hotel to the meeting (join-in) point at Bitexco Financial Tower, No. 2 Hai Trieu Street, District 1,
                Ho Chi Minh City and must be there before 7.45 AM.<br>The tour guide and the coach will meet and
                pick him up on Monday at 7:45 AM at this meeting point.<br>Price: USD 82 x 8 days + USD 30 x 7
                nights (single supplements) + USD 50 (pre tour hotel) + USD 50 (post tour hotel) + USD 50 x 2 rounds
                (transfers)
            </p></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-md-block"><img class="w-100 h-auto" src="img/Exp1.webp" alt=""></div>
    </div>
