            <p class="text-success fw-bold fs-3">
                Example 2: A London couple want to book 12-day holiday in Malaysia and they agree to combine 2 tour
                lines Malaysia North and Malaysia South.
            </p>
            <p>
                They arrange their own flights to/from London and Kuala Lumpa of Malaysia.<br>Since their first
                visit to the country, they book through Fun Asia Tour Pre/Post tour hotel accommodation and
                transfers.<br>They book and paid and have got a Tour Voucher for the tour and an email to confirm
                their booking for Pre/Post Tour hotel rooms and airport pick-up and transfers.<br>Since they book
                the tour line together with Pre/Post hotel and transfers, they make payments for both the tour and
                Pre/ Post hotel rooms and transfers.<br>15 days before they arrive in KL, they send an email
                to
                <a href="mailto:ops@funasiago.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ops@funasiago.com</a> to
