                (Double): USD 48/night and Pre-tour airport–hotel transfer: USD 23/ trip.<br>The Post tour hotel
                room: USD 48/night and Hotel-Airport transfer: USD 23/ trip<br><br>Total tour price: USD 82 x
                11 days + USD 48 x 2 (Pre/Post hotel) + USD 23 x 2 (transfers).
            </p></div>
    </div>
